test_negate_of_lists:
assert [6] == [-6]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != -6
  Full diff:
  - [-6]
  ?  -
  + [6]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [6] == [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 0
  Right contains 6 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
  + [6]
test_non_divisibles_1:
assert [6] == []
  Left contains one more item: 6
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [6]
  ?  +
